      "content": "Hey, I'm starting to put together the slides for the Sequoia meeting next week. Can you pull together a summary of our growth metrics from last quarter? I need a high-level overview of the MRR and user acquisition trends to show them the momentum we've built. Needs to look really polished for the deck.",
