      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"migrating to premium\"? I don't recall seeing any upgrade confirmations for those specific accounts in the CRM. If Sequoia asks for a breakdown of our retention vs. new acquisition, and they see the churn rate for mid-market was actually quite high last month, it’s going to look like we're hiding something. Are you sure we can frame this as an \"upgrade\" rather than just losing customers? I don't want to get grilled in due diligence if the numbers don't line up.",
